uring readability. I'm also working on the data source display with its database icon and text formatting, considering how to present the \"Bound Integrations\" list effectively.\n\n\n**Evaluating Performance Metrics**\n\nI'm now integrating performance metrics into the inspector panel, including \"Synthesis Accuracy\" and \"Telemetry Baseline,\" to provide real-time feedback. I'm focusing on concise presentation, utilizing specific visual cues like icons and color-coded text within a clearly styled section. I'm ensuring these elements are accessible and easily interpretable, integrating them alongside other existing data.\n\n\n"}}
